28/2/24

arm is in smartphones,refridgerators etc..
it begins in 1980s
the british computer manufacturer was in need of processor,the acorn archimedes
they wanted processor to deliver high performance and energy efficient
architecture- specifies how a processor behave
it specifies -instruction set,register set,exception model,memory model,debug
RISC-reduced instruction set computer,simple instructions,simple addressing modes,load store architecture
micro architecture-the build and design of a processor is micro architecture
ip core=implementation in VHDL or verilog of block of hardware logic
profiles-application profile,real time profile,microcontroller profile
ARM license their IP to customors
companies other than ARM purchase architecture and implement their own design
